title: Week Six: What we learned
text:
We are now headed into week seven of the 2015 Arkansas high school football season, and there have been a lot of things I have learned after six weeks of play in each classification. 
CLASS 7A 
Fayetteville, Bentonville, and Har-Ber are doing their typical 7A West dance. Har-Ber knocked off Bentonville last night, and Fayetteville has dominated everyone in their path thus far. The Purple Dogs will lock it up with Har-Ber this week, then with Bentonville in week 10, so it is still anyone's game in that conference.
